{"tid":1057642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大灣區】土耳其商人涉逃稅遭公安拘留。土商恐慌 ：「以後不再到中國」","createTime":"2019-03-12T04:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T04:53:13.000Z","uid":202464,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8219f4dfdb5e141960af0500dfc0cadb643735cb","tid":1057642,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:32:33.000Z","msg":"土耳其媒體報道，參加福建廈門國際石材展覽會的4名土耳其商人遭控逃稅，在廈門遭到拘留。消息引發其他土耳其商人恐慌，部份石材公司老闆提前改搭航班離開當地，甚至稱以後不會到中國。<br />\n<br />\n土耳其「自由日報」（Hurriyet Daily News）報道，身份未被揭露的4名商人上周六（9日）清晨在下榻的酒店遭警方拘留。被拘人士屬3家在中國設有辦事處的土耳其公司員工，警方同時查扣了相關文件和物品。"},{"pid":"843ff57cb8d94029d62d8ffe3634b6c94e1172e3","tid":1057642,"uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"犯法咪捉人囉<br />\n有乜問題先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efef29b3b4a001936af74999ceb99603d00c102","tid":1057642,"uid":60092,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"俾你班火雞見識下咩叫以法治國!!!"},{"pid":"3a9625c33ea282d5a22ad53c23ef9ef5d41f7391","tid":1057642,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37240a86362609b4c33069da5d5cff1e19a429cd","tid":1057642,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"大突厥主義 vs 大中華主義"},{"pid":"8f239851ec4cb2e52f9f2c3b74f2768c83ff3da4","tid":1057642,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"加拿大<br />\n土耳其<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個清單慢慢加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe5a81c50c3b13a1576a3ecadaea6d0e8bd0a7","tid":1057642,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:41:48.000Z","msg":"好人好者怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class